# Local data and generated artifacts.
# The whole top-level data/ tree stays untracked: source datasets (e.g. gated
# LMSYS-Chat-1M) must never be redistributed through this repository. The
# leading slash keeps src/longfeedback/data (the adapter package) tracked.
/data/
artifacts/**
!artifacts/.gitkeep
reports/generated/
*.parquet
*.arrow

# Experiment services and credentials
.env
wandb/
mlruns/
